
SQUID PBI README
--------------------------------------------

-- Running Squid --

To start or stop squid, you may use the PC-BSD Services GUI (Start -> System Settings -> Services Manager)
or, via the command-line ( # /Programs/rc.d/squid start / stop )

-- Configuring Squid --

The configuration files for this squid PBI are located in /Programs/etc/squid. These config files
will not be removed when you uninstall squid, which allows you to upgrade squid easily without having
to re-create your configuration. 

